[[File:Tribunemeeting.jpg|thumb|right|A meeting of the Tribunal, left to right: [[Plumba]], [[General/Legends|General]] [[Paltr Carvin]] and [[Challer]]]]
'''Tribune''' was the title given to certain high-ranking members of the [[Imperial Ruling Council/Legends|Imperial Ruling Council]] between the removal of [[Sate Pestage/Legends|Sate Pestage]] from the [[Galactic Emperor/Legends|Imperial throne]] and the rise of [[Ysanne Isard]]. The Council was at this point ruled by an inner circle known as the '''Tribunal''', which was presided over by Tribune [[General/Legends|General]] [[Paltr Carvin]] and included his civilian advisers, Tribunes [[Challer]], and [[Plumba]].

